---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Cookie Policy - Agra Astro">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Cookie Policy</h1>
    
    <div class="prose max-w-none">
      <p class="mb-6">Last updated: December 17, 2024</p>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">1. What Are Cookies</h2>
        <p>Cookies are small text files that are stored on your computer or mobile device when you visit our website. They help us:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>Remember your preferences</li>
          <li>Understand how you use our website</li>
          <li>Improve your browsing experience</li>
          <li>Provide personalized content and advertisements</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">2. Types of Cookies We Use</h2>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">2.1 Essential Cookies</h3>
        <p class="mb-4">These cookies are necessary for the website to function properly. They enable basic functions like page navigation and access to secure areas of the website.</p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">2.2 Analytics Cookies</h3>
        <p class="mb-4">We use analytics cookies to understand how visitors interact with our website. This helps us improve our website's functionality and content.</p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">2.3 Advertising Cookies</h3>
        <p class="mb-4">Through Google AdSense, we use advertising cookies to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>Show relevant advertisements</li>
          <li>Measure ad performance</li>
          <li>Prevent the same ad from appearing too often</li>
          <li>Understand your interests and preferences</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">3. Google AdSense</h2>
        <p>We use Google AdSense to display advertisements. Google uses cookies to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>Serve personalized ads based on your interests</li>
          <li>Track ad impressions and clicks</li>
          <li>Measure the effectiveness of advertisements</li>
          <li>Prevent fraudulent advertising activity</li>
        </ul>
        <p>You can learn more about Google's advertising cookies at <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700">Google's Advertising Policies</a>.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">4. Managing Cookies</h2>
        <p>You can control and manage cookies in various ways:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>Browser Settings: You can modify your browser settings to accept or reject cookies</li>
          <li>Google Ad Settings: Visit <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700">Google Ad Settings</a> to manage your ad preferences</li>
          <li>Third-party Tools: Use various opt-out tools provided by advertising networks</li>
          <li>Private Browsing: Use your browser's private/incognito mode</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">5. Impact of Disabling Cookies</h2>
        <p>If you choose to disable cookies:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>Some website features may not function properly</li>
          <li>Your preferences may not be saved</li>
          <li>You may see less relevant advertisements</li>
          <li>Your browsing experience might be affected</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">6. Updates to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Cookie Policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">7. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about our Cookie Policy, please contact us at:</p>
        <ul class="list-none pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>Email: privacy@agraastro.com</li>
          <li>Phone: +91 1234567890</li>
          <li>Address: [Your Address], Agra, India</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
